Class WorkspaceView

java.lang.Object
  com.compendium.core.datamodel.WorkspaceView
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class WorkspaceView
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

The WorkspaceView object represents a open ViewFrames in Compendium with scrollbar positions and reference to child View Note: This class is a holding container only and does not currently write to the database
